thread.title: Inez Brown
thread.title_full: Primo Print reviewed by Inez Brown

author: Inez Brown
title: Inez Brown
text: We are absolutely pleased with the quality of the Sweet 16 "Save the Date" cards I created for my niece; the colors are beautiful and reflect girly pretty Sweet 16! The team was extremely helpful in ensuring the files submitted were in the proper format for the type of printing I requested. Great job PRIMO PRINT! Will be recommending the company for sorority projects.
